data.description: You're going to LOVE this 3 bedroom 2.5 bath updated split-level house.  Kitchen is open to the living room making it the perfect space for entertaining.  Kitchen has granite, stainless steel appliances and a large island.  Fenced backyard with a large deck.  Beautiful hardwood floors in the living room and down the hallway.  Upstairs bathroom vanities have granite also. Finished basement has a fireplace and half bathroom.
